classes\ that\ reside\ in\ a\ package\ '..shared.domain..'\ and\ have\ simple\ name\ ending\ with\ 'Aggregate'\ should\ have\ modifier\ FINAL,\ because\ \u805A\u5408\u6839\u987B\ final\uFF0C\u9632\u6B62\u5B50\u7C7B\u7834\u574F\u4E0D\u53D8\u91CF\uFF1B\u5DF2\u77E5\u8FDD\u89C4\ CampaignAggregate\ \u975E\ final\ \u5F85\ T10\ \u91CD\u5199\u65F6\u4FEE\u590D=b0a56989-fafe-4843-bfd4-a9dfe64e536c
